{
  "name": "Pinterest WF2 - Publish via Tailwind",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Pinterest – Workflow 2: Publish approved pins (daily)\n\nReads the **Pinterest Pins** tab, takes rows where **Approval = Approved** and **Status = Review**, resolves the **Board name -> Board ID** (from Tailwind Boards), and schedules each pin in **Tailwind** at its **Scheduled Date** (Tailwind publishes it then). Writes back Status / Pin URL / Error / Pinned Time.\n\n**Setup:** Google Sheets + Tailwind (Bearer) credentials. Set accountId in Set Config.",
        "height": 396,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "78b79f84-0052-4a45-9ab1-5bed7e789785",
